  "texts": [
    "Our BERTopic model identified 101 topics, along with a significant group of outliers (48.89% of tweets).",
    "While merging outliers with other topics was possible, we chose not to do so in order to preserve the cluster quality.",
    "Among the 101 identified topics, the most frequent was AI and ChatGPT with 22,836 tweets (7.26%).",
    "We excluded this topic from the subsequent analysis to focus on tweets discussing specific applications and aspects of ChatGPT, rather than ChatGPT itself.",
    "An example tweet from this topic is \"ChatGPT knows it best!\""
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}